---
import OriginalLayout from '../layouts/OriginalLayout.astro';
import '../styles/original/method.css';
---
<OriginalLayout title="Method – SOS Magic" page="method">
<main class="method-page">

    <section id="section-1" class="method-section">

      <div class="method-hero">

        <div class="method-kicker">
          <span class="method-line-small" data-text="The S.O.S. Magic">The S.O.S. Magic</span>
          <span class="method-line-big" data-text="METHOD">METHOD</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="method-title">Your Emotional First Aid</h1>

        <p class="method-text">
          Find out how the Complete Digital Interpretation Books and their Neon Decks work together to support you.
        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="method-video">
        <div class="video-shell">
          <video class="method-player"
                 src="https://sosmagic.b-cdn.net/videos/method.mp4"
                 poster="https://sosmagic.b-cdn.net/videos/method.png"
                 controls
                 playsinline
                 preload="metadata" aria-label="Page introduction video">
          </video>
        </div>
      </div>

    </section>

    <section id="section-2" class="method-section">

      <h1 class="method-title">
        From Mental Noise to Inner Silence and Clarity in Minutes
      </h1>

      <p class="method-text">
        This is your guide to the subconscious depths where your true answers wait.
      </p>

      <p class="method-text">
        By reconnecting with your intuition, you reclaim the confidence you need to feel grounded and finally tune into your own frequency.
      </p>

      <div class="method-image">
        <img src="https://sosmagic.b-cdn.net/fotos/Photo%2023-02-2026%2C%2015%2056%2006.png" alt="Section 2 visual"/ alt="" aria-hidden="true">
      </div>

    </section>

    <section id="section-3" class="method-section">

      <div class="method-hero">

        <div class="method-kicker">
          <span class="method-line-mid" data-text="Why it works?">Why it works?</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="method-title">The Three Layers of Your Transformation</h1>

        <p class="method-text">
          This journey is an effortless, science-backed method designed to bypass mental resistance
          through three visual layers:
        </p>

        <div class="method-accordion" aria-label="Three layers accordion">

          <div class="method-acc-item">
            <button class="method-acc-btn" type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="layer-1">
              <span class="method-acc-bullet" aria-hidden="true">1</span>
              <span class="method-acc-title">Neon Glow: Your Mental Reset</span>
            </button>
            <div class="method-acc-panel" id="layer-1" hidden>
              <p class="method-text">
                Acts as a lighthouse in the dark, helping you find your way during moments of uncertainty.
                This layer breaks the anxious loop and gives your mind the immediate calm it needs to stop
                struggling.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="method-acc-item">
            <button class="method-acc-btn" type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="layer-2">
              <span class="method-acc-bullet" aria-hidden="true">2</span>
              <span class="method-acc-title">Neuro-aesthetic Art: Deep Immersion</span>
            </button>
            <div class="method-acc-panel" id="layer-2" hidden>
              <p class="method-text">
                Specially crafted visual art captures your focus and holds it. This allows your real feelings to
                surface from the depths, bypassing the noise of daily stress.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="method-acc-item">
            <button class="method-acc-btn" type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="layer-3">
              <span class="method-acc-bullet" aria-hidden="true">3</span>
              <span class="method-acc-title">The Mermaid Archetype: Inner Safety</span>
            </button>
            <div class="method-acc-panel" id="layer-3" hidden>
              <p class="method-text">
                Familiar since childhood, these images help the conscious mind relax. By lowering your inner
                critic and reducing the need for control, they clear the way for intuition and positive change.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <p class="method-text" style="margin-top: 24px;">
          The S.O.S. MAGIC Method is more than just cards; it is a tool to tune into your own frequency
          and reclaim your confidence through the subconscious.
        </p>

        <p class="method-text" style="font-weight: 700;">
          Its effectiveness is trusted by our global community of 150,000+ women.
        </p>

      </div>

    </section>

    <section class="method-section method-footer-section">

      <p class="method-text method-footer-note">
        For more information about the S.O.S MAGIC Method, please check our
        <a href="/faq">FAQ</a>.
      </p>

      <div class="method-footer-image">
        <img
          src="https://sosmagic.b-cdn.net/fotos/Photo%2001-03-2026%2C%2006%2024%2020%20(10).png"
          alt=""
          loading="lazy"
        / alt="" aria-hidden="true">
      </div>

    </section>

  </main>

<script is:inline src="/scripts/method-accordion.js" defer></script>
</OriginalLayout>
